---
title: "SSD UC2 — Generate Story from Voice Input"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as ":User"
    participant S as ":System"

    Note over User,S: System treated as BLACK BOX<br/>UC2 — Generate Story from Voice Input (extends UC1)

    User->>S: clickVoiceInput()
    S-->>User: recorderStarted, recorderState: "listening"

    User->>S: submitVoiceAudio(audioFile: WAV)
    S-->>User: transcriptionResult(text, language, confidence)

    alt confidence < threshold OR text is empty
        S-->>User: error("Could not transcribe audio")
    end

    User->>S: confirmTranscription(transcribedText)
    S-->>User: promptReceived, promptType

    loop system generating story
        S-->>User: progressUpdate(stage, message)
    end

    S-->>User: storyGenerated(storyId, title, scenes[], pdfPath)
